<h1>Audit (A-06-13-00032)</h1>

<h2>08-07-2014<br />
Illinois' Federal Medicaid Withdrawals Were Supported by Net Expenditures for Fiscal Years 2010 Through 2012</h2>

<h2 class="line">Complete Report</h2>

<p class="download">Download the 

